Hi Don,
Yes, according to the VW bus parts book we have there is a differance.  Yes,
they will fit onto a 1955-63, but if you are going for a full blown NOS or
good used resto it will be incorrect.  We do not know what the differance is
except for the part number, and no they are not part of the M216 suspension.
How much is the seller asking?  We have several sets of perfectly good used
ones to sell/trade since we have gone to the later 1964-67 suspensions in
our
1960-63 buses.   Eric&Barb

